{
  "page": "List of characters created for A Song of Ice and Fire Roleplaying",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><br />\nThis page lists the characters that have been created for <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire_Roleplaying\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire Roleplaying\">A Song of Ice and Fire Roleplaying</a></i>, a roleplaying game based on the <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire\">A Song of Ice and Fire</a></i> fantasy series by <a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a>, who have no equivalent counterpart in the books.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Characters_from_A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire_Roleplaying\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Characters from <i>A Song of Ice and Fire Roleplaying</i></span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#House_Orlych_of_Rimehall\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">House Orlych of Rimehall</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Characters_from_Peril_at_King.27s_Landing\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Characters from <i>Peril at King's Landing</i></span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#House_Dannett\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">House Dannett</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#House_Lugus\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">House Lugus</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Characters_from_Wedding_Knight\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Characters from <i>Wedding Knight</i></span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#House_Harte\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">House Harte</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#House_Manning\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">House Manning</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#Others\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Others</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Characters_from_A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire_Roleplaying\">Characters from <i>A Song of Ice and Fire Roleplaying</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_characters_created_for_A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire_Roleplaying&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Characters from A Song of Ice and Fire Roleplaying\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"House_Orlych_of_Rimehall\">House Orlych of Rimehall</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_characters_created_for_A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire_Roleplaying&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: House Orlych of Rimehall\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li>Lord Brandon Orlych, Lord of Rimehall\n<ul><li>Lady Mercena Karstark, Lady of Rimehall, formerly of a lesser branch of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Karstark\" title=\"House Karstark\">House Karstark</a>\n<ul><li>Ser Gerald Orlych, heir to Rimehall</li>\n<li>Lady Rene Orlych, daughter of Rimehall</li></ul></li>\n<li>Ser Byron Rivers, <a href=\"/index.php/Hedge_knight\" title=\"Hedge knight\">hedge knight</a></li>\n<li>Ser Deved Joren, <a href=\"/index.php/Household_knight\" title=\"Household knight\">household knight</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Master-at-arms\" title=\"Master-at-arms\">master-of-arms</a></li>\n<li>Mikael, master of the hunt</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">Maester</a> Tyren, formerly of a lesser branch of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\">House Frey</a></li></ul></li></ul>\n<h2><span id=\"Characters_from_Peril_at_King's_Landing\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Characters_from_Peril_at_King.27s_Landing\">Characters from <i>Peril at King's Landing</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_characters_created_for_A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire_Roleplaying&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Characters from Peril at King&#039;s Landing\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"House_Dannett\">House Dannett</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_characters_created_for_A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire_Roleplaying&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: House Dannett\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li>Lord Alfric Dannett, a widower\n<ul><li>Adham Dannett, his son</li>\n<li>Iris Dannett, his daughter, now a <a href=\"/index.php/Prostitute\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Prostitute\">prostitute</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>\n<ul><li>Ruben Piper, Iris's former betrothed</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"House_Lugus\">House Lugus</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_characters_created_for_A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire_Roleplaying&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: House Lugus\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li>Lord Konrad Lugus\n<ul><li>Lady Luisa Lugus, formerly of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Clegane\" title=\"House Clegane\">House Clegane</a>\n<ul><li>Ser Naton Lugus, their son and heir\n<ul><li>Kitha, kitchen wench, and mother of one of Naton's <a href=\"/index.php/Bastard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastard\">bastards</a></li>\n<li>Salia, Kitha's daughter, and mother of one of Naton's bastards</li></ul></li>\n<li>Orton Lugus, their second son</li>\n<li>Liesa Lugus, their eldest daughter, Lady of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Broom\" title=\"House Broom\">House Broom</a></li>\n<li>Marita Lugus, their second daughter, twice a widow\n<ul><li>Langley Woods, Marita's new betrothed</li>\n<li>Glarus Ptek, of <a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavos</a>, Marita's lover</li></ul></li>\n<li>Ludviga Lugus, their youngest daughter</li></ul></li></ul></li>\n<li>Klaas Lugus, Konrad's older brother, mysteriously died after a minor injury</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Characters_from_Wedding_Knight\">Characters from <i>Wedding Knight</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_characters_created_for_A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire_Roleplaying&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Characters from Wedding Knight\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"House_Harte\">House Harte</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_characters_created_for_A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire_Roleplaying&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: House Harte\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li>Lord Gerard Harte\n<ul><li>Lady Ella Harte, his wife\n<ul><li>Sylvie Harte, their oldest daughter, betrothed to Kevan Manning</li>\n<li>Eilene Harte, their younger daughter</li></ul></li>\n<li>Etan Hogg, household knight and ward of Lord Harte, and Sylvie's lover</li></ul></li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"House_Manning\">House Manning</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_characters_created_for_A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire_Roleplaying&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: House Manning\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li>Lord Artur Manning, a widower\n<ul><li>Kai Manning, his eldest son, died in battle</li>\n<li>Ser Kevan Manning, his second son and heir, betrothed to Sylvie Harte</li>\n<li>Darren Manning, his third son</li></ul></li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Others\">Others</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_characters_created_for_A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire_Roleplaying&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Others\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Septon\" title=\"Septon\">Septon</a> Moor</li>\n<li>Maester Hamdan</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403134544\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.016 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.045 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 42/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 73/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate